      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been comprehensively overhauled, rod bearings replaced, and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014addressing all critical E46 platform concerns. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling characteristics these cars are renowned for. A truly turn-key, concours-level specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
