      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time capsule. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and pampered since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero swirls, chips, or imperfections, while the wheels are entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the leather remains supple and taut, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma, with every electronic component and switch functioning perfectly. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. Complete with all original manuals, two keys, and a comprehensive service history, this car is ready for a discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
